<tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><img border="0" src="../triangle.JPG"><font size="3" face="Tahoma" color="#004242"><b>SHADOWBOUND GLOVES</b></font></p></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Class:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><b>Necromancer</b></font></td></tr> <tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Minimum Level:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">24</font></td></tr> <tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Estimated Quest Length:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">5 hours</font></td></tr> <tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Quest NPC:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Syllina</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Starting Zone:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><a href="../zones/zoneinfo.asp?Zone=Temple of Solusek Ro&Comment=1">Temple of Solusek Ro</a></font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Secondary Zones:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><a href="../zones/zoneinfo.asp?Zone=Guk, Lower&Comment=1">Guk, Lower</a></font></p><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><a href="../zones/zoneinfo.asp?Zone=Rathe Mountains&Comment=1">Rathe Mountains</a></font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Items Needed:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Inky Shadow Silk</font></p><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Scepter of Tears</font></p><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Hand of Shadow</font></p><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Skeletal Finger</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Description:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><b>1.</b> Head to the Temple of Solusek Ro and talk to <b>Syllina</b>.  You can find her at loc +320 +80.  She will tell you that she makes three different kinds of ShadowBound armor, Boots, Gloves, and Robes.  You will need a different set of items to get each of these items.
<br><br>
<b>2.</b> To get the ShadowBound Gloves, you need the following items: an Inky Shadow Silk, the Scepter of Tears, a Hand of Shadow, and a Skeletal Finger.
<br><br>
<b>3.</b> You can get these items in any order, but remember that items gotten from the Shadow Men disappear once you logout.
<br><br>
<b>4.</b> The <b>Inky Shadow Silk</b> must either be tailored or bought from a PC.  To tailor one, you will need <b>1 Shadow Wolf Pelt</b> (uncommon drop off Shadow Wolves), <b>2 Gather Shadows scrolls</b> (bought in any Necromancer guild), and <b>1 Silk Swatch</b> (tailored from 2 Spider Silk, sometimes dropped by Large Spiders/Giant Spiders).
<br><br>
<b>5.</b> The <b>Scepter of Tears</b> can be found in Guk.  Go to Guk and zone in the first zone to Lower Guk.  Turn left in the first intersection and look for a waterfall.  When you find it, look for a room with a carpet on the floor and you will see a Scepter.  That is the one you are looking for.  Cast Identify on it to make sure you have the right one.
<br><br>
<b>6.</b> The <b>Hand of Shadow</b> is dropped by <b>Shadowed Men</b>.  Keep killing them until you get one.
<br><br>
<b>7.</b> Finally, the <b>Skeletal Finger</b> is dropped by <b>Giant Skeletons</b>.  Head to an area where Giant Skeletons spawn (Rathe Mountains for example) and keep killing them until you get one.  It is an uncommon drop.
<br><br>
<b>8.</b> Once you have all four items, head back to the Temple of Solusek Ro and give all four items to <b>Syllina</b>.  In return, she will give you the ShadowBound Gloves.</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Author:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Wraith (Bristlebane)</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Quest Reward:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><b>ShadowBound Gloves</b></font></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma"></font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><b>AC+6, STR+3, DEX+3, INT+3, Mana+3</b></font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Rating:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><b>7.2</b> (average of <b>6</b> votes)</font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left" colspan="2"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top" align="left" valign="middle"><b><font size="2" face="Tahoma">Rate this quest:</font></b></td><td width="80%" valign="top" align="left" valign="middle"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><FORM ACTION = "ratequest.asp" METHOD = post><SELECT NAME="Voting"><OPTION VALUE="0">Rate this Quest</OPTION><